  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for uriparser",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for uriparser fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-42371: numeric truncation in text range comparison when an application accepts URIs with a length in\n  gigabytes (bsc#1262999).\n- CVE-2026-44927: truncation of `ptrdiff_t` to `int` in various places (bsc#1264578).\n- CVE-2026-44928: function family `EqualsUri` can misclassify two unequal URIs as equal (bsc#1264579).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
